mao 's last dancer ( simplified chinese : &lt;unk&gt; ; traditional chinese : &lt;unk&gt; ; pinyin : mao mao &lt;unk&gt; ) is a 2008 australian drama film directed by bruce beresford . the film was selected as the australian entry for the best foreign language film at the 58th academy awards , but was not accepted as a nominee . the film was selected as the australian entry for the best foreign language film at the 89th academy awards but it was not nominated .